1. Users should be able to find the food by food name. They should be able to put some filters on search
on MealType: Veg or Non-Veg, CuisineType: a particular set of cuisine e.g. (Italian + German)
2. For the fetched food items, users should be able to navigate to the corresponding restaurant, check the
menu/price list, add items to their cart and place an order.
3. Different modes of payment i.e NetBanking, CardBased Payment etc should be supported.
4. A cart can't contain foodItems from multiple restaurants.
5. Users should be able to search for restaurants by their names. They should also be able to put some
filters on the search like Veg/Non-Veg, a particular cuisine etc...
6. Users should be able to modify their cart i.e. add/remove foodItems or their quantities.
7. The system should contain important information about the users like delivery address, phone number
to ensure delivery.
8. User should be able to track order status: ORDER PLACED, COOKING, READY_FOR_DELIVERY, OUT_FOR_DELIVERY,
DELIVERED. In addition to these, a user can also cancel an order if the COOKING has not started, that will
change the order status to CANCELED
9. The system should also provide ETA for delivery.
10. User should be able to provide rating feedback for the order.
11. Restaurants should be able to register themselves to the system. Admin approval needed.
12. Restaurants should be able to update costings, food item availability, open/close time etc...